title: The.Real.Housewives.Of.New.Jersey.S06E05.One.Flew.Over.The.Chick
description:
Tempers are still fiery as the first responders party comes to a dramatic conclusion. Amber's husband Jim goes on the offensive with Teresa Aprea, while Nicole demands loyalty from her boyfriend Bobby. Dina tries to warm up to a new man in her life, but her feelings towards her ex still flicker within. Melissa and Amber have a sitdown to hash out just who started the rumor heard round the Jersey grapevine.

Thanks to ROCKSTER!!!!!
